.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-NOTES" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-notes \- list ledger entries that have notes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-notes
.RI [ wallet ]
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns all ledger entries with a non-empty
.B note
field, newest first.
Default limit is 50.
Returns an empty array if the wallet database does not exist.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{entry_id, note, created_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-tag (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-ledger-search (1)
